SET versions = '[{"author":"Default — $20 Voucher","content":"Hello, is this XXX?\n\nI''ll just keep this call short, less than a minute. Understand that you are studying or working now?\nI''m calling to inform you that you have qualified to win a $20 Capitaland vouchers from us.\n\nIt might have been some time back, and you are one of the lucky winners.\n\nI know you''re very busy, so to help you redeem the $20 voucher, all we have to do is just to conduct a quick zoom session with you on how to grow your money faster than the bank.\n\nAfter the session, we will also pass you a copy of our free investment guidebook.\n\nI''ll just set the session tentatively this saturday morning at 10am over zoom, and we can always confirm closer to the date, is that okay?\n\nAnd after this call, I''ll send you a whatsapp to confirm, and you just need to help me to reply the message is that okay?\n\nSo just one last thing, this session is just for you to learn more, So as long as you learn something that''s beneficial for you, then that''s good enough! Just to check, how do I address you? (if no name). (key it into the CRM)\n\nOne last thing, as long as you learn something from the session, then that''s good enough! So see you this [date/time], and have a good day!\n\n---\n\n**Where are we from / how you get my number:**\nWe are from themoneybees, we are a financial education platform for young adults. You might have clicked on an ad a while back."},{"author":"MBS Staycation Version","content":"Hello, is this [Name]?\n\nGreat! I''ll keep this really short—less than a minute. Just wanted to check, are you currently working or studying?\n\nI''m calling because you''ve been selected as one of the lucky winners eligible to redeem a chance to win a 2D1N Marina Bay Sands staycation for two, through a quick financial education campaign we''re running.\n\nYou may have filled out a quick online survey with us some time back, and we''re reaching out to help you complete the final step to enter the draw.\n\nTotally understand if you''re busy! So to make it super easy, all we need is a quick Zoom session where we''ll share how you can grow your money faster than what most banks offer. 📈\n\nAt the end of the 20-minute session, you''ll:\n\n✅ Secure your entry for the staycation draw\n📘 Receive our free investing guidebook\n💡 Get tips on how to start growing your wealth early\n\nI''ll go ahead and tentatively schedule the session for this Saturday at 10AM, and we can always adjust if needed—does that sound okay?\n\nAfter this call, I''ll drop you a quick WhatsApp to confirm the session. Could you help me reply to that when it comes in? 😊\n\nAnd just to clarify, the session is purely educational—there''s no obligation or commitment. As long as you learn something helpful for your finances, that''s already a win!\n\nJust before I let you go—how should I address you again? (If not already named—record in CRM)\n\nAwesome, looking forward to meeting you this [Date & Time]. Have a great day ahead!\n\n---\n\n❓ **If they ask where you got their number:**\n\nYou actually clicked on one of our ads recently—it was about a staycation giveaway or financial survey. We''re from TheMoneyBees, a financial education platform that helps young adults learn how to manage and grow their money wisely."},{"author":"$20 Facebook Voucher — Text from FB","content":"Hi [Name],\n\n[name] from TheMoneyBees Here! 😊\n\nYou did a quick survey online for you to redeem a $20 Capitaland voucher.\n\nJust want to check if I got the right person?\n\n[wait for reply]\n\nGreat!\n\nI''ll help you redeem it through a quick zoom session where we''ll share some helpful tips on how to grow your money faster than just saving in the bank as well 💰\n\nHere''s what you can gain after the 30 minute zoom session.\n\n🔥 Access to hours of materials from the world''s best minds in our community\n\n🧠 Learn the money language schools never teach\n\n🌟 Strategies to fast-track your wealth, passively.\n\nAs a bonus, you will also get these resources after the consultation\n\n![Free Ultimate Guide to Adulting](/scripts/free-adulting-guide-promo.png)\n\n![Free Ultimate Guide to Investing](/scripts/free-investing-guide-promo.png)\n\nI''ve scheduled your session for [Confirmed Date & Time A], or [Confirmed Date & Time B] will any of these timings work for you?\n\nJust reply \"A\" or \"B\" to indicate which time you prefer so that I can send reminders and notifications leading up to the dates"}]'::jsonb,
